<br />
Description: This ability lends persistence to your illusionary disguises, causing them to last until you die or manually remove them. 
<br />

<br />
-This means when we zone we will have the same illusion and if we log we will come back as the same illusion?
<br />

<br />
-Does this AA mean we can buy illusion potions then be that race until we die or manually remove them?</span></td>
